
stool parts.blend

The average commercial bar is 100 to 110 cm off the ground, which suggests a height of 75-90cm.
A kitchen bar is more likely 90cm off the ground, and usually needs a stool of 65cm to 70 cm.
Most stools have a seat width of something like 35cm, assuming they have no back.

Seat of stool           1
base underneath stool   2
Leg                     3
Rod 1                   4
Rod 2                   5
